<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=LP_record&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: History and physical aspects">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="History_and_physical_aspects">History and physical aspects</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=LP_record&action=edit&section=2.php.html" title="Edit section: Soundtrack discs">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Soundtrack_discs">Soundtrack discs</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg/220px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg" width="220" height="146" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg/330px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg/440px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Neumann_Cutting_Machine_01.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<a href="Georg_Neumann" title="Georg Neumann">Neumann</a> Record Cutting Machine</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg/220px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg" width="220" height="146" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg/330px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg/440px-Neumann_Cutting_Machine_02.jpg 2x" /></a>
